AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' SAN JOSE ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT.ARRIVAL_TIME > = 2130 AND FLIGHT.ARRIVAL_TIME < = 2230 ) ) ) ) ) ;

DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME IN ( SELECT DATE_DAY.DAY_NAME FROM DATE_DAY WHERE DATE_DAY.YEAR = 1993 AND DATE_DAY.MONTH_NUMBER = 5 AND DATE_DAY.DAY_NUMBER = 10 ) ) AND NOT ( ( FLIGHT.DEPARTURE_TIME > FLIGHT.ARRIVAL_TIME AND ( FLIGHT.TIME_ELAPSED > = 60 OR FLIGHT.ARRIVAL_TIME < 41 ) AND 1 = 1 ) ) ) OR ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME IN ( SELECT DATE_DAY.DAY_NAME FROM DATE_DAY WHERE DATE_DAY.YEAR = 1993 AND DATE_DAY.MONTH_NUMBER = 5 AND DATE_DAY.DAY_NUMBER = 9 ) ) AND ( FLIGHT.DEPARTURE_TIME > FLIGHT.ARRIVAL_TIME AND ( FLIGHT.TIME_ELAPSED > = 60 OR FLIGHT.ARRIVAL_TIME < 41 ) AND 1 = 1 ) ) ) ) ) ) ;

what is a flight , that goes from baltimore to san francisco and arrives at san francisco at eight p m on a friday ||| ( SELECT DISTINCT FLIGHT.FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT WHERE ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' BALTIMORE ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' SAN FRANCISCO ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT.ARRIVAL_TIME = 2000 AND ( ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' FRIDAY ' ) AND NOT ( ( FLIGHT.DEPARTURE_TIME > FLIGHT.ARRIVAL_TIME AND ( FLIGHT.TIME_ELAPSED > = 60 OR FLIGHT.ARRIVAL_TIME < 41 ) AND 1 = 1 ) ) ) OR ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' THURSDAY ' ) AND ( FLIGHT.DEPARTURE_TIME > FLIGHT.ARRIVAL_TIME AND ( FLIGHT.TIME_ELAPSED > = 60 OR FLIGHT.ARRIVAL_TIME < 41 ) AND 1 = 1 ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ;

CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' TORONTO ' ) ) AND FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' SAN DIEGO ' ) ) ) ) ) ; 

what does l a x stand for ||| ( SELECT DISTINCT AIRPORT.AIRPORT_NAME FROM AIRPORT WHERE AIRPORT.AIRPORT_CODE = ' LAX ' ) ; 

could you show me the meals for these flights ||| ( SELECT DISTINCT FOOD_SERVICE.MEAL_CODE , FOOD_SERVICE.MEAL_NUMBER , FOOD_SERVICE.COMPARTMENT FROM FOOD_SERVICE WHERE FOOD_SERVICE . MEAL_CODE IN ( SELECT FLIGHT . MEAL_CODE FROM FLIGHT WHERE ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' DENVER ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' DALLAS ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' MONDAY ' ) OR ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' TUESDAY ' ) OR ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' WEDNESDAY ' ) OR ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' THURSDAY ' ) OR FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' FRIDAY ' ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ; 

what does u a stand for ||| ( SELECT DISTINCT AIRLINE.AIRLINE_NAME FROM AIRLINE WHERE AIRLINE.AIRLINE_CODE = ' UA ' ) ;

AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' PHOENIX ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' DENVER ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' MONDAY ' ) OR ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' TUESDAY ' ) OR ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' WEDNESDAY ' ) OR ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' THURSDAY ' ) OR FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' FRIDAY ' ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ; 

does the phoenix airport have ground transportation to and from downtown ||| ( SELECT DISTINCT GROUND_SERVICE.CITY_CODE , GROUND_SERVICE.AIRPORT_CODE , GROUND_SERVICE.TRANSPORT_TYPE FROM GROUND_SERVICE WHERE ( GROUND_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' PHOENIX ' ) AND GROUND_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE IN ( SELECT AIRPORT . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT WHERE AIRPORT . AIRPORT_CODE IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' PHOENIX ' ) ) ) ) ) ;

CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' DALLAS ' ) ) AND ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' MONDAY ' ) OR ( FLIGHT . FLIGHT_DAYS IN ( SELECT DAYS . DAYS_CODE FROM DAYS WHERE DAYS.DAY_NAME = ' FRIDAY ' ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ) ; 

may i see all nonstop flights from saint petersburg to , charlotte ||| ( SELECT DISTINCT FLIGHT.FLIGHT_ID FROM FLIGHT WHERE ( FLIGHT.STOPS = 0 AND ( FLIGHT . FROM_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' ST. PETERSBURG ' ) ) AND FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' CHARLOTTE ' ) ) ) ) ) ; 

could you tell me what the abbreviation u s stands for ||| ( SELECT DISTINCT AIRLINE.AIRLINE_NAME FROM AIRLINE WHERE AIRLINE.AIRLINE_CODE = ' US ' ) ;

what is the meaning of meal code s ||| ( SELECT DISTINCT FOOD_SERVICE.MEAL_DESCRIPTION FROM FOOD_SERVICE WHERE FOOD_SERVICE.MEAL_CODE = ' S ' ) ;

AIRPORT_CODE FROM AIRPORT_SERVICE WHERE AIRPORT_SERVICE . CITY_CODE IN ( SELECT CITY . CITY_CODE FROM CITY WHERE CITY.CITY_NAME = ' OAKLAND ' ) ) AND FLIGHT . TO_AIRPORT IN ( SELECT AIRPORT_SERVICE . what does the airline code d l stand for ||| ( SELECT DISTINCT AIRLINE.AIRLINE_NAME FROM AIRLINE WHERE AIRLINE.AIRLINE_CODE = ' DL ' ) ; 

what airline uses the code h p ||| ( SELECT DISTINCT AIRLINE.AIRLINE_NAME FROM AIRLINE WHERE AIRLINE.AIRLINE_CODE = ' HP ' ) ; 

what does the meal code s slash stand for ||| ( SELECT DISTINCT FOOD_SERVICE.MEAL_DESCRIPTION FROM FOOD_SERVICE WHERE FOOD_SERVICE.MEAL_CODE LIKE '% S / %' ) ;
